      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"http://lucianocuicaplay.blogspot.com/2012/05/dom-um-romao.html\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a1/Dom-um_%282%29.jpg/300px-Dom-um_%282%29.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"227\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/a/a1/Dom-um_%282%29.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Dom-um_(2).jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Dom Um Romão <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dom_Um_Rom%C3%A3o\">Dom Um Romão</a>, (August 03, 1925 – July 27, 2005)<br />\nwas a Brazilian  <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jazz\">jazz</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Drummer\">drummer</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Percussion_instrument\">percussionist</a>.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Category:Dom_Um_Rom%C3%A3o&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Image from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://lucianocuicaplay.blogspot.com/2012/05/dom-um-romao.html\">Dom Um Romão | Blog do Cuíca Play</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301152140\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.009 seconds